---
title: Honey Mustard Pork Tenderloin with Roasted Potatoes and Green Beans
description: This easy and savoury honey vinaigrette acts as a zippy flavour booster for pork chops. Paired with blistered green beans and roasted potatoes, it's the ultimate dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-mustard-pork-tenderloin-8680939f.jpg
